Localization.Name: Clark Defense Systems
Localization.Description:
Ground-combat defensive systems, covers a lot of commercial territory from personal armor to defense systems. Naming convention tend to be pretty straight-forward and logical.

Models: PAB-4 (Personal Ablative/Ballistic Light Armor)

QDB-12 QuiKCade (Quick Deployment Barricade)

Localization.Name: Novikov Backpack Patina
Localization.Description:
Item Type: Heavy Backpack
Carrying Capacity: 180K µSCU
Core Compatibility: Heavy

Confidently explore cold environments while wearing the Novikov. Caldera designed a spacious backpack to compliment this advanced exploration suit, so those venturing across unknown terrain can bring enough supplies to survive the journey.

The Patina edition offers a grounded look combining soft teal with bronze.
